世界.<br />\n<br />\n若老師對學生有私心, 實不會以正常心態去幫學生改卷, 特別係寫文的科目.<br />\n咁對學生好不公平的."},{"pid":"ce1873c5e8a2c44b5a7e0aab9d054960a02fa83f","tid":736321,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"killer+學生質素（維護killer ge狗太多）"},{"pid":"7a574a8eba85c559c46d1989e18fc62458a217a7","tid":736321,"uid":193157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"學費貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7e742f85090c16dc585be98e6644456621c6e0","tid":736321,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"讀SPACE至少都可以話自己係HKU仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHKU仔但SPACE到讀啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b13149f16475d3abf4ef1e93668b7ec6195031a","tid":736321,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"發現d 人BBB都入到Nursing, 身邊SPACE 嘅同學要爆4先得"}]}